author: National Geographic
description:
What does it mean to be reunited with someone you didn’t dare hope to see again? When the 2004 Indian Ocean Tsunami struck Phi Phi Island, Soffie was swept into its inescapable current. Trapped and unable to move, she fought to survive. She was certain she’d lost everything. But in the aftermath, when all seemed lost, the impossible happened.

Witness stories of hope, hardship, and heroism from the 2004 Indian Ocean Tsunami in Tsunami: Race Against Time, now streaming on Disney+ and Hulu.
